reviewText: This exercise program is great for those looking to enjoy a soothing spiritual experience during your daily workout. There are several levels to try depending on your fitness needs.

This workout gives an excellent workout for people at all levels! Tonya is an awesome personal trainer! So if you ever get the chance to work with her personally, I highly recommend you do. However, the dvd is a good substitute! I recommend it!

Toning Your Temple DVD has allowed me the opportunity to workout in the comfort of my home. Mrs Iverson's easy step by step instructions were very simple to follow. I've recommended this item to many others to purchase. It is extremely helpful for the individuals that has busy schedules with their careers and families. Thanks
This is an excellent workout, It is very effective for me and a lot of fun.  I encourage others to try it.
